Before launching a mystery shopping survey, clearly outline what you want to measure. Are you looking to improve customer service or optimise store layout? Or there can be other goals like evaluating staff behavior, ensuring compliance with brand standards, Etc. Defining goals will help you choose the right mystery shopping company in India and design a tailored evaluation process.

